                        <msContents>
                            
                            <summary>Reports of a buffalo fight at <placeName>Semabok</placeName> on Saturday last. Two manuscripts discussing a buffalo fight
                                related to padi planting ceremonies. Notes on the government file indicate that these two MSS were collected in response
                                to a request from <persName>Hervey</persName> dated <date>18 June 1890</date>
                                Includes correspondence with members of the Malacca police office. A police report in Romanised Malay describes the nature of the buffalo fight, 
